OL,3,CJersey elite swimmer woke up with
OL,4,CFrench accent after stroke
OL,6,FFormer elite swimmer Jack Allan
OL,7,Fdeveloped a French accent after a
OL,8,Fsudden stroke which left him paralysed
OL,9,Fand unable to talk.
OL,11,FThe 21-year-old from Jersey suffered
OL,12,Fbrain damage following a kick to the
OL,13,Fhead during a mixed martial arts
OL,14,Fsession last October.
OL,16,FHe explains: "Some artery near the
OL,17,Fcentre of my brain burst and they
OL,18,Fcouldn't perform surgery. They just
OL,19,Fhad to cross their fingers and hope."
