OL,3,CJersey elite swimmer woke up with
OL,4,CFrench accent after stroke
OL,6,FJack slowly started to recover and
OL,7,Fweeks later, when he managed to regain
OL,8,Fsome speech, he woke up one day to
OL,9,Ffind that he had developed a French
OL,10,Faccent.
OL,12,FJack had Foreign Accent Syndrome, a
OL,13,Frare condition that changes a person's
OL,14,Fspeech patterns to make it sound as
OL,15,Fthough they are speaking in a non-
OL,16,Fnative way.
OL,18,FHe needed speech therapy to relearn
OL,19,Fhis original voice.
