OL,3,CJersey elite swimmer woke up with
OL,4,CFrench accent after stroke
OL,6,FBefore his accident, Jack represented
OL,7,FJersey at the 2022 Commonwealth Games
OL,8,Fin Birmingham, finishing fifth in the
OL,9,F4x100m medley relay, and also competed
OL,10,Fat the Island Games in Gotland and
OL,11,FGibraltar.
OL,13,FJack is now using that determination
OL,14,Fhe needed as a sportsman to focus on
OL,15,Fhis rehab.
OL,17,FHe explains: "As you said high
OL,18,Fachieving, hard working, that just
OL,19,Ftranslated to the recovery. I would
OL,20,Fsay, 'why be negative, what's the
OL,21,Fpoint?'"
